<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT41">
<l>kāṇa luṟukiṉṟēṉ kallaruvi muttutira,</l>
<l>vōṇa viḻavi loliyatira pēṇi</l>
<l>varuvēṅ kaṭavāveṉ ṉuḷḷam pukuntāy</l>
<l>tiruvēṅ kaṭamataṉaic ceṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You from Vēṅkaṭam to which [devotees] come in a cherishing way,</l>
<l>As pearls drop off from the resounding waterfalls</l>
<l>and produce echo during the ōṇam festival! You have entered my heart.</l>
<l>I desire to go and see that sacred Vēṅkaṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
